(define/contract (maximum-sum-queries nums1 nums2 queries)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) (listof exact-integer?) (listof (listof exact-integer?)) (listof exact-integer?))
  (let* ((n (length nums1))
         (sums (map + nums1 nums2))
         (sorted-sums (sort sums >))
         (indexed-sums (map list sums (range n)))
         (sorted-indexed-sums (sort indexed-sums (lambda (x y) (> (car x) (car y)))))
         (prefix-max (make-vector n))
         (max-so-far -1))
    (for ([i (in-range n)])
      (set! max-so-far (max max-so-far (car (list-ref sorted-indexed-sums i))))
      (vector-set! prefix-max i max-so-far))
    (map (lambda (query)
           (let* ((xi (first query))
                  (yi (second query))
                  (valid-indices (filter (lambda (idx)
                                           (and (>= (list-ref nums1 (cadr idx)) xi)
                                                (>= (list-ref nums2 (cadr idx)) yi)))
                                         sorted-indexed-sums)))
             (if (null? valid-indices)
                 -1
                 (vector-ref prefix-max (cadr (car valid-indices))))))
         queries)))
